originalText.text: I’ve been very impressed with Dr. Laurie Mullen’s care. In my first exam she took the time to listen to my concerns and chiropractic goals. She asked great questions and was very thorough. Her care shows concerns for the whole body and she has a genuine desire to help me heal. Dr. Mullen uses multiple strategies and techniques that are best for MY body. Her care is customized and unique for each patient. At the front desk Tara is super friendly and helped me with all my insurance questions. This practice is a great place for all your chiropractic care!

originalText.text:
I have experienced very good results from being treated by Dr. Laurie Mullen. She takes longer with her patients than most chiropractors. She combines gentle manipulation along with muscle work and massage to achieve results. She is a good listener and can challenge your thinking, offer encouragement and is dedicated to the patient’s well-being. Her office assistants are pleasant, helpful and will work to find you an appointment.

I was referred to Dr. Mullen by two friends one of whom had debilitating back pain to the point that it interfered in his personal day to day living and his work life. He achieved excellent results and is now able to function normally.
